<br>
I'm ally to Tormax. Believe you only need amiable to complete it though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufrosin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Frosin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 9:09:04 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quick Tormax Faction.</span><hr size=1> High amiably near kindly for Frostbringer / cloak ask him 'what axe' and see if he give you the quest.<br>
